				<td colspan="2"><div class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">ok, so its legal to drink  what is the difference between smoking weed and drinking? what is worse for your health? i think weed is no more addictive than alchohol and just as unhealthy-if not worse. smoking weed can actually be good for you. if your tense, sit back and smoke some herb, and you feel at ease. 
