				<td colspan="2"><div class="postbody">Would legalizing it make the world a better place? no
<br />
The only reason drugs are illegal and alcohol isn't, is that drinking was around way before our country, but the drugs came into the society later. Saying something is equally bad is a terrible defence. Personally I think the world needs less of all the types of drugs, even the legal ones, specially those stupid depression pills that are all mental effect. But I guess the world will never be rid of the desire for a quick fix, and some people see drugs as the quick fix, but they aren't.<span class="gensmall"></span>


