				<td colspan="2"><div class="postbody">Well I have not much to say that Trysbrina has not said already, except for the fact that "marijuana" is a slang name for Cannabis, used to associate the plant with mexican consumers.
<br />

<br />
Calling it "marijuana" is racist, wether intentional or not by anyone using that word. (and as far as 'racist' things go this is pretty mild)
<br />
The proper name is Cannabis Sativa and Cannabis Indica.
<br />

<br />

